node.text:
CROQUE MONSIEUR CROISSANT LASAGNA

INGREDIENTS
* 	10 shop-bought all-butter croissants
* 	a little butter for greasing
* 	1 1/2 cups bechamel sauce
* 	2 cups grated emmental cheese
* 	10 slices wafer thin cooked ham, plus a little more for layering
* 	nutmeg, a scrape
* 	dijon mustard, 1/2 tsp per croissant

node.text:
These balls are our favourite!

CROQUE MONSIEUR MASH BALLS
INGREDIENTS
* 6 cups cold leftover mash
* 4 slices ham, chopped into small cubes
* 3 cups grated emmental
* 2 tbsp dijon mustard
* 1/4 cup finely chopped parsley
* 1 tbsp salt
* 1 tbsp pepper
* 1 cup flour
* 4 eggs, beaten with a little milk
* 2 cups panko breadcrumbs
* Enough groundnut oil to deep fry

This Skillet Queso Chicken is the absolute ONE!
INGREDIENTS
* 3 chicken breasts
* 1 pack taco seasoning
* 2 mixed peppers, diced
* 2 jalapeno peppers, diced
* 1/2 cup tomato salsa
* 1 tsp chipotle sauce
* 1 tsp salt
* 1 cup double cream
* 3 cups grated red cheddar
* Chopped tomatoes
* Chopped avocados
* Crumble nachos
* Chopped coriander

INGREDIENTS
* 	10 shop-bought all-butter croissants

* 	10 slices wafer thin cooked ham, plus a little more for layering

* 	dijon mustard, 1/2 tsp per croissant

* 4 eggs, beaten with a little milk
* 2 cups panko breadcrumbs

What’s better than Mac n cheese? 🧀
Mac’n’cheese BURGERS 🍔 
•
INGREDIENTS
400g cooked macaroni noodles
1 1/2 cups bechamel sauce
1 1/2 cups grated cheddar
1 cup grated mozzarella cheese
10 Bacon rashers, cooked and chopped finely
500g beef mince
2 tsp salt
1 1/2 pepper
1 tsp garlic powder
4 eggs, whisked
2 cups flour
2 cups seasoned breadcrumbs
Oil for frying
#twistedfood #food #yummy #burgerrecipe #dinnerideas #macncheese #nomnom

You asked for more veggie recipes and boy have we DELIVERED - Save our 4 all time best vegetarian recipes! Here are the ingredients - save the post to your food folder!

Crispy Stuffed Mushroom Burgers

INGREDIENTS
8 Portobello mushroom caps
1 1/2 cup Mixed cheddar
1 cup mozzarella
1/2 parmesan
6 rashers cooked bacon, chopped (optional!)
2 cloves garlic, minced
1/4 cup chopped chives
1/2 tsp pepper
3/4 cup mayonnaise
Egg Wash
Seasoned Flour
Panko breadcrumbs
Frying oil
Burger toppings

GARLIC MOZZARELLA TOMATO SOUP DIPPERS
INGREDIENTS
24 slices soft white bread
24 pieces pizza mozzarella
1/4 cup flour
1/4 cup water
2 cups finely grated parmesan cheese
1 tsp pepper
1 tbsp finely chopped parsley
1 1/2 tsp garlic powder
Tomato sauce
Oil for frying
3 cups mized tomatoes, quartered if large
4 cloves garlic
1 yellow onion, chopped
3 tbsp olive oil
1 tsp salt
1 tsp pepper
1 tsp sugar
8 slices cheddar or mozzarella cheese
1 3/4 cups vegetable stock

Grilled Cheese Tomato Soup Hedgehog Bread
INGREDIENTS
6 plum tomatoes, halved
10 cherry tomatoes
1 beefsteak tomato, quartered
4 cloves garlic
1 yellow onion, chopped
3 tbsp olive oil
1 tsp salt
1 tsp pepper
8 slices cheddar or mozzarella cheese
1 3/4 cups vegetable stock
1 loaf soft French bread loaf
1/4 cup butter, melted
3 crushed garlic cloves
Handful finely chopped parsley

Veggie Big Macs
INGREDIENTS
SERVES 4/ MAKES 4 BURGERS!
* 	2 tins black beans in salted water, rinsed and drained
* 	2 spring onions, finely chopped
* 	2 tbsp parsley, finely chopped
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	1 large egg
* 	100g dried breadcrumbs
* 	2 tbsp sunflower oil, for frying
For the sauce:
* 	1 tsp white wine vinegar
* 	1 tsp pickle brine
* 	1/2 tsp sweet smoked paprika
* 	1/2 cup mayonnaise
* 	1/2 tsp sugar
* 	1/2 tsp garlic powder
* 	1/2 tsp onion powder
* 	1 tsp dijon mustard
For the bun:
* 	6 pre-sliced burger buns (1 1/2 per person)
* 	8 slices american cheese
* 	lettuce, shredded
* 	chopped white onion
